Meet @lauragift_, the newest member of the GitHub Stars Program ⭐. Gift is a frontend engineer and technical writer passionate about web accessibility and building dev communities—and loves geeking out on photography 📷. Check out her GitHub Star profile.

Gift Egwuenu | GitHub Stars
I'm a Frontend Engineer passionate about making the web accessible to everyone & an advocate for building developer communities. I enjoy creating content this includes technical tutorials, video tutorials, and content about my life as a developer. I'm a Media Developer Expert at Cloudinary, and an Auth0 Ambassador, Microsoft MVP, and Nuxt.js Ambassador.
When I'm not coding you can find me geeking about photography and exploring different ways of documenting stories using photography and cooking delicious delicacies.
